Summary: Saw a triangular shaped object fly past in a east to west direction
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my way to a local store on an errand, as I usually do I take my digital camera with me (I recently took amateur photgraphy) on the way there I was snapping photos of the area as it looks at night for an online photo album. As I came home I had my attention diverted to the sky and there I saw a triangular shaped object silenty going along. The lights on it were very visable and since there was a little bit of light still in the sky you could make out a very dull black color. I took pictures of the object and will include them if requested. This is not the first time I have seen this object, but have kept it to myself, although this is the first time I have had the chance to take pictures of the object.
